{"word":"προσκάθημαι","slug":"προσκάθημαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσκάθημαι</b></el> <el>(ionic <el>-κάτημαι</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>properly <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> of <a href='S:προσκαθέζομαι'><el>προσκαθέζομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be seated by</i> or <i>near, live with</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theophrastus'>Theophr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to sit down against</i> a town, <i>besiege</i> it, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>obsidere</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}